{"id":232348081,"title":"#集點 超商點數","content":"只有我覺得便利商店集點數很黑嘛.....\n\n每次為了換超商點數的商品就努力集點數\n\n可是要去換的時候店員就會說：\n\n這個是限量的耶，開始沒多久就已經沒了哦\n\nWTF？活動不是才剛開始跑嘛？\n\n是誰集點數集這麼快的啊⋯⋯\n\n問了一下會不會再進貨\n\n得到的答覆是，我們這家很多天沒進貨了哦\n\n可以去其他間便利商店詢問看看\n\n好吧，既然沒進貨了，那我也認了....\n\n過沒幾天去超商買東西在排隊等待結帳時\n\n怎麼看到妳從底下拿出我要換的「點數商品」\n\n就這樣給了那個人進行兌換？？？\nhttps://i.imgur.com/hhgq5Bn.jpg\n\n\n來說說你們的經驗吧⋯⋯","excerpt":"只有我覺得便利商店集點數很黑嘛.....，每次為了換超商點數的商品就努力集點數，可是要去換的時候店員就會說：這個是限量的耶，開始沒多久就已經沒了哦，WTF？活動不是才剛開始跑嘛？是誰集點數集這麼快的啊","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ffc2ebb1-9985-4ce8-8f30-7dfdca609afa","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-22T02:49:32.035Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-22T02:49:32.035Z","commentCount":12,"likeCount":22,"tags":[],"topics":["超商板","點數"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"超商","forumAlias":"cvs","school":"中國科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":22}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/hhgq5Bn.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"6eea4bf2-043f-4fe7-8e7d-5e330aeeb2b7","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hhgq5Bnl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/hhgq5Bnl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hhgq5Bnl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-22T02:49:32.035Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-22T02:49:32.035Z"},{"id":"6eea4bf2-043f-4fe7-8e7d-5e330aeeb2b7","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hhgq5Bn.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/hhgq5Bn","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hhgq5Bnl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-22T02:49:32.035Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-22T02:49:32.035Z"}],"postAvatar":""}